      "review_summary": "The PR changes main-session restart recovery to re-present the last user message for inspectable text-only assistant tails, expands structured text/tool-call detection, and adds regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +223, Tests +489. Total +712 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main reads the recent transcript, returns a resume block reason for an assistant or stale approval tail, sends the unresumable resend notice, and marks the session failed. I did not run a live gateway-restart reproduction in this read-only review.",
